---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Rooftop | HALM Collective">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Rooftop</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Enjoy panoramic views and fresh air from our stunning rooftop space.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our rooftop area offers a unique perspective and versatile space for various activities. Whether you're looking to work outdoors, join a fitness class, or simply enjoy a sunset with friends, our rooftop provides the perfect setting.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Rooftop Features</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Lounge Area</h3>
          <p>Comfortable seating for relaxation and socializing with panoramic views.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Outdoor Fitness</h3>
          <p>Regular rooftop yoga, meditation, and fitness classes when weather permits.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Evening Events</h3>
          <p>Special sunset gatherings and nighttime community events.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Working Space</h3>
          <p>Outdoor tables and power outlets for those who want to work with a view.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Rooftop Schedule</h2>
      <p>Check our calendar for upcoming rooftop events and activities.</p>
      
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/schedule" class="text-primary hover:underline">View Schedule</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
